                       |BKB-= |CKBExit Message |BKB=-
               
|MKOExmess is the command used to change your exit message that
only thieves will see when you log off of Darkwind. Exmess
followed by no value will reset your exit message to the standard
message. Exmess <message> will set your exit message correctly.
Placing a $N in the message will put your name into the exit
message, just as it does when setting your title when you advance
a level.

|CKOGLVL required: |GKB1
|CKOSyntax: |YKOexmess <message>                |CKOCost: |WKOFree
